{"tid":266263,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【時裝車禍】簡單配搭都會出錯：不能相愛的涼鞋與長襪","createTime":"2017-06-01T10:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T12:52:26.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f14ca446be649a4de406a2215207ad059e3c8b8a","tid":266263,"uid":731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"所謂的時裝車禍，普遍都萬變不離其宗，一律都犯下了眼高手低的錯誤。但是哪些「車禍」是屬於舞台級的，只能保持遠觀距離。談及與我們生活相關的「車禍」例子，或許你與我都曾經犯下這些小錯誤。例如是以襪子配搭涼鞋等等的組合，往往最多人嘗試，但卻最少人成功。<br />\n<br />\n男士們想一嘗涼鞋滋味，但卻生怕變成「阿伯」，所以人人都買入一雙以運動鞋與涼鞋混種的忍者鞋，當時成為了一時佳話。但普遍人人只配了一對花襪，甚至bare foots，入選成為男友/ 女友的NG（出事）配搭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qE4FK3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qE4FK3&d=X1LzviS17SySsPZJwcPYbxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=93ed62ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qE4FK3</a>"},{"pid":"168266ea113c9e4cf0543667d4da50246bb5c791","tid":266263,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"涼鞋襯短襪我 like 喎。"},{"pid":"324f1f39388d150508041c7967b9cccccc4e37ff","tid":266263,"uid":110271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"涼鞋已經冇緊嚴重<br />\n拖鞋先核突"},{"pid":"f27b15f910c12e89e021df91913f510202761224","tid":266263,"uid":25753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"好想試 y3 qasa sandals + 黑襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e76be9f94a810786994b44eb2b03d8598b48bdf","tid":266263,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>涼鞋襯短襪我 like 喎。</blockquote><br />\n都見你成日發表偉論，睇嚟你啲taste都<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}